&lt;p&gt;    &#8230;te argument&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;ol&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;What is the purpose of the change&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ol&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    This PR modifies the JobDetails constructor to verify that the `tasksPerState` array size is equal to `ExecutionState.values().length`. The array contains the number of tasks in each execution state, and it thus required that the sizes match.&lt;/p&gt;


